themselves with religion and politics into

00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:51.623
she'owl during Matsah perfecting if you

00:18:51.663 --> 00:18:55.163
will the certainly making not guilty the

00:18:55.203 --> 00:18:57.605
children of the covenant as a result those

00:18:57.644 --> 00:18:59.846
who acknowledge and accept what father and

00:18:59.885 --> 00:19:00.786
