00:19:04.971 --> 00:19:06.951
and to be adopted into his family.

00:19:06.971 --> 00:19:10.892
That is how the three spring, Miqraey,

00:19:11.592 --> 00:19:12.992
Pesach, Matsah, and Bikuwrym,

00:19:13.492 --> 00:19:16.353
enable the benefits of the covenant,

00:19:17.554 --> 00:19:18.193
all five of them.

00:19:20.054 --> 00:19:23.295
So Dowd epitomizes, and much of his life,

00:19:23.315 --> 00:19:23.855
Yisrael,

00:19:23.875 --> 00:19:26.576
and probably more so after his horrid

00:19:26.596 --> 00:19:27.855
affair with Bathsheba,

00:19:29.393 --> 00:19:32.256
And he is also, on the positive side,

00:19:32.296 --> 00:19:35.458
the exemplar of the covenant of how we

00:19:35.519 --> 00:19:37.440
can be wrong and made right.

00:19:37.740 --> 00:19:41.663
How we can fall and be raised back

00:19:41.763 --> 00:19:41.923
