00:19:49.450 --> 00:19:52.112
To be averse to the covenant or to

00:19:52.173 --> 00:19:53.413
Dowd, well,

00:19:53.433 --> 00:19:56.455
that will exclude a soul from the presence

00:19:56.496 --> 00:19:56.836
of God.

00:19:57.708 --> 00:20:00.367
because he favors and cherishes his

00:20:00.448 --> 00:20:06.028
covenant and his son above all others.

00:20:06.048 --> 00:20:06.169
Now,

00:20:06.229 --> 00:20:09.430
Dowd approached Yahowah intellectually,

00:20:09.470 --> 00:20:13.691
but also emotionally, even experimentally.

00:20:14.211 --> 00:20:17.830
He knew exactly what he was doing most

00:20:17.871 --> 00:20:20.571
of the time and why it was important.

00:20:21.011 --> 00:20:22.852
And he was fully cognizant,

00:20:22.951 --> 00:20:24.792
a great deal of his life,

00:20:25.373 --> 00:20:26.512
of what the result would be.

00:20:27.471 --> 00:20:29.993
He was a wholehearted participant and

00:20:30.074 --> 00:20:33.076
genuinely devoted to the relationship.

00:20:34.056 --> 00:20:34.676
And as such,

00:20:34.717 --> 00:20:37.137
he engaged doing what his father desired.

00:20:38.179 --> 00:20:40.901
And those who fail to appreciate this and

00:20:40.941 --> 00:20:44.323
misconstrue Dowd's life and the purpose of

00:20:44.363 --> 00:20:45.222
the covenant, well,

00:20:45.723 --> 00:20:48.605
they do so to their own detriment.

00:20:48.625 --> 00:20:48.945
Therefore,

00:20:48.965 --> 00:20:50.646
it would be fair to say that we

00:20:50.686 --> 00:20:55.910
approach Yahowah by what Moseh wrote about

00:20:57.002 --> 00:20:59.844
and what Dowd has accomplished.

00:20:59.864 --> 00:21:04.065
They're hand in glove, aren't they?

00:21:04.184 --> 00:21:06.164
It is as it should be, really.

00:21:07.885 --> 00:21:09.425
As it was with Dowd,

00:21:10.185 --> 00:21:11.747
so can it be with us.

00:21:12.707 --> 00:21:15.788
Yahowah introduced Himself to us in His

00:21:15.847 --> 00:21:16.248
Towrah,

00:21:16.387 --> 00:21:19.308
and He proved His existence through His

00:21:19.368 --> 00:21:19.828
prophets.

00:21:20.597 --> 00:21:23.578
He has provided all of the information we

00:21:23.618 --> 00:21:25.519
need to exercise good judgment.

00:21:26.040 --> 00:21:28.080
To determine what is right and wrong about

00:21:28.121 --> 00:21:28.461
God.

00:21:28.981 --> 00:21:32.242
Now this process is interactive.

00:21:32.983 --> 00:21:35.765
With Yahowah revealing and us observing and

00:21:35.845 --> 00:21:37.846
responding.

00:21:37.905 --> 00:21:39.446
Both have to happen.

00:21:39.487 --> 00:21:40.446
God's done his part.

00:21:40.666 --> 00:21:41.488
Now it's up to you.

00:21:42.847 --> 00:21:45.710
Now Yahowah designated and equipped us for

00:21:45.769 --> 00:21:46.589
this purpose.

00:21:47.410 --> 00:21:48.330
The ninth

00:21:49.525 --> 00:21:49.744
Mizmowr

00:21:49.785 --> 00:21:50.404
reads,

00:21:51.346 --> 00:21:54.286
For you have acted upon and engaged in

00:21:54.385 --> 00:21:57.967
my decision-making process regarding my

00:21:58.027 --> 00:22:00.307
means to resolve disputes.

00:22:01.127 --> 00:22:04.209
ʿAsah means to act, to engage, to do,

00:22:04.288 --> 00:22:05.230
to work.

00:22:06.230 --> 00:22:10.851
And Mishpat is a compound of my to

00:22:10.891 --> 00:22:13.271
ponder the implications of Shaphat,

00:22:13.432 --> 00:22:15.393
which is to decide,

00:22:15.653 --> 00:22:16.992
to exercise good judgment.

00:22:19.921 --> 00:22:22.402
And my ability to judge and to be

00:22:22.461 --> 00:22:23.281
judgmental,

00:22:24.061 --> 00:22:26.442
distinguishing between right and wrong,

00:22:27.202 --> 00:22:28.663
wa dyn 'any

00:22:29.084 --> 00:22:32.125
And we know of the man named Daniel.

00:22:32.164 --> 00:22:34.625
Well, Daniel would be,

00:22:36.105 --> 00:22:38.307
my God is judgmental.

00:22:38.487 --> 00:22:39.846
Dyn means to judge,

00:22:39.886 --> 00:22:43.067
to distinguish between right and wrong,

00:22:43.327 --> 00:22:46.229
to differentiate between true and false.

00:22:49.574 --> 00:22:51.635
God here, or certainly Dowd,

00:22:51.836 --> 00:22:53.137
is saying that if you want to have

00:22:53.178 --> 00:22:54.398
a relationship with God,

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:56.260
you ought to judge.

00:22:57.201 --> 00:22:58.443
If you do not judge,

00:22:58.663 --> 00:22:59.644
you will be judged.

00:22:59.884 --> 00:23:02.709
It's the opposite of what is presented in

00:23:02.729 --> 00:23:03.869
the Christian New Testament.

00:23:06.553 --> 00:23:07.232
He goes on to say,

00:23:07.272 --> 00:23:08.554
and you have been established,

00:23:09.173 --> 00:23:11.714
or you have established the approach to

00:23:11.775 --> 00:23:13.914
the seat of honor, the kise.

00:23:14.734 --> 00:23:16.435
The seat of honor is the mercy seat

00:23:16.476 --> 00:23:17.556
of the Ark of the Covenant.

00:23:17.615 --> 00:23:19.336
It is also Dowd's throne,

00:23:19.416 --> 00:23:22.117
and it will be Dowd's throne forevermore.

00:23:23.857 --> 00:23:26.538
The idea that you have restored and

00:23:26.598 --> 00:23:29.339
established that is from Yashab,

00:23:29.440 --> 00:23:33.580
which is deduced from the remnant found in

00:23:33.641 --> 00:23:36.281
Cave Eleven of Qumran.

00:23:38.205 --> 00:23:40.067
So you have established the approach to

00:23:40.127 --> 00:23:42.269
the seat of honor, the throne.

00:23:42.671 --> 00:23:45.192
You have decided and judged correctly.

00:23:45.634 --> 00:23:47.194
shaphat tsedeq.

00:23:47.295 --> 00:23:49.136
You have rendered the right decision.

00:23:49.156 --> 00:23:51.519
You have been just, rational, and fair.

00:23:51.940 --> 00:23:54.903
This is also from 11QPs,

00:23:55.304 --> 00:23:59.087
where shaphat is second-person perfect.

00:23:59.107 --> 00:23:59.548
It's Mizmowr

00:23:59.587 --> 00:24:01.230
Lyrics to sing nine-four.

00:24:02.625 --> 00:24:06.627
So this is about acting upon our best

00:24:06.667 --> 00:24:07.128
judgment,

00:24:07.269 --> 00:24:11.511
us making informed and rational decisions.

00:24:11.613 --> 00:24:15.256
This was and will always be the way

00:24:15.296 --> 00:24:19.179
that the ultimate judge will render our

00:24:19.199 --> 00:24:19.538
fate.

00:24:20.380 --> 00:24:22.300
And if we come to know him,

00:24:23.082 --> 00:24:24.583
listen to what he has to say,

00:24:24.663 --> 00:24:26.224
observe what he has written,

00:24:26.625 --> 00:24:28.946
process it intelligently, act upon it,

00:24:29.728 --> 00:24:29.968
then

00:24:30.682 --> 00:24:32.944
Rather than being judged, he'll say, hey,

00:24:32.984 --> 00:24:34.445
you want to sit next to me here

00:24:34.625 --> 00:24:35.707
on the bench?

00:24:36.707 --> 00:24:38.167
There is no evidence against you.

00:24:38.288 --> 00:24:38.769
Obviously,

00:24:38.828 --> 00:24:40.670
all of it was taken into Sheowl to

00:24:40.710 --> 00:24:41.971
be deposited by Dowd.

00:24:42.531 --> 00:24:44.712
And we can just smile and cozy up

00:24:44.792 --> 00:24:46.555
and say, that'll be great.

00:24:47.734 --> 00:24:50.356
The path to knowing Yahowah, therefore,

00:24:50.657 --> 00:24:52.659
and understanding what he is offering and

00:24:52.679 --> 00:24:55.840
what he expects in return is not through

00:24:55.901 --> 00:24:56.481
obedience.

00:24:57.001 --> 00:24:57.942
It is not through faith.

00:24:59.005 --> 00:25:00.465
Yahowah provided His Towrah,

00:25:00.726 --> 00:25:02.686
teaching His naby, prophets,

00:25:02.787 --> 00:25:04.048
and Mizmowr songs,

00:25:04.827 --> 00:25:06.929
so that we could be thoughtful and

00:25:06.969 --> 00:25:08.730
discerning in our response to Him.

00:25:09.911 --> 00:25:10.570
As a result,

00:25:10.671 --> 00:25:13.353
the process to the desired result

00:25:14.012 --> 00:25:16.835
necessitates listening before speaking,

00:25:17.934 --> 00:25:20.457
observing before engaging.

00:25:22.917 --> 00:25:24.378
The pronouns, I think,

00:25:24.419 --> 00:25:25.818
are particularly telling in this

00:25:25.858 --> 00:25:26.220
statement.

00:25:27.078 --> 00:25:29.280
Dowd used you three times,

00:25:29.361 --> 00:25:31.281
indicating that he is addressing Yahowah,

00:25:32.022 --> 00:25:34.865
showing that God acted and engaged based

00:25:34.904 --> 00:25:37.066
upon Dowd's judgment,

00:25:37.385 --> 00:25:40.509
that God established the seat of honor and

00:25:40.548 --> 00:25:42.910
that he rendered the right decision.

00:25:43.510 --> 00:25:44.612
Me was used twice,

00:25:44.672 --> 00:25:47.212
speaking of himself in ways that we are

00:25:47.252 --> 00:25:49.434
more accustomed to seeing God.

00:25:49.494 --> 00:25:50.256
For example,

00:25:50.816 --> 00:25:53.617
it is Dowd's Mishpat decision-making

00:25:53.657 --> 00:25:56.259
process regarding the means to resolve the

00:25:56.660 --> 00:25:59.805
disputes between God and man that Yahowah

00:25:59.924 --> 00:26:01.067
is acting upon.

00:26:01.407 --> 00:26:04.291
This means that Dowd was far more than

00:26:04.352 --> 00:26:06.095
just the Passover lamb,

00:26:06.895 --> 00:26:10.520
since the Father was enabling their

00:26:10.580 --> 00:26:11.663
combined plan.

00:26:13.116 --> 00:26:14.258
Dowd had thought it through.

00:26:15.038 --> 00:26:16.680
He was determined that by his

00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:17.721
participation,

00:26:18.422 --> 00:26:20.784
the most beneficial result would be

00:26:20.844 --> 00:26:21.365
achieved.

00:26:22.025 --> 00:26:22.164
Now,

00:26:22.286 --> 00:26:24.968
this did not come to him until very

00:26:25.228 --> 00:26:27.130
late in his life.

00:26:28.010 --> 00:26:30.353
And so he's being highly reflective at

00:26:30.393 --> 00:26:34.297
this point based upon what he had learned.

00:26:34.875 --> 00:26:36.596
And I think, actually,

00:26:37.116 --> 00:26:39.279
while I had previously thought that the

00:26:39.420 --> 00:26:43.463
Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr was written in year

00:26:43.523 --> 00:26:44.565
three thousand Yah,

00:26:44.605 --> 00:26:49.288
serving as the cornerstone of that year of

00:26:50.170 --> 00:26:53.334
the exact same amount of time from

00:26:54.737 --> 00:26:56.137
Eden and back to Eden,

00:26:56.397 --> 00:26:57.938
right there in the heart,

00:26:57.978 --> 00:26:59.959
three thousand years into the six thousand

00:26:59.979 --> 00:27:00.519
year plan.

00:27:01.898 --> 00:27:03.380
I no longer think that's the case.

00:27:03.420 --> 00:27:04.900
In fact, I'm rather sure of it.

00:27:05.779 --> 00:27:08.040
The Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr was a

00:27:08.080 --> 00:27:12.281
collaborative effort between Eythan Ha Ezrachy

00:27:12.342 --> 00:27:14.042
and Yahowah,

00:27:15.363 --> 00:27:17.223
whereby it was used

00:27:18.044 --> 00:27:22.766
to restore Dowd's relationship with Yahowah

00:27:23.306 --> 00:27:24.826
so that he would know exactly who he

00:27:24.906 --> 00:27:28.528
is and what he was to achieve and

00:27:28.647 --> 00:27:31.150
I think it was delivered at least four

00:27:31.210 --> 00:27:34.211
years and maybe six and eight years prior

00:27:34.270 --> 00:27:36.392
to the end of Dowd's first of three

00:27:36.451 --> 00:27:41.314
lives and that this Mizmowr would therefore

00:27:41.334 --> 00:27:44.454
have been written after it so that Dowd

00:27:44.474 --> 00:27:46.395
had a chance to think these things through

00:27:47.813 --> 00:27:50.215
He now knew God's plan.

00:27:50.896 --> 00:27:54.361
He had been presented exactly who he was,

00:27:54.421 --> 00:27:55.301
what he would achieve,

00:27:55.342 --> 00:27:56.323
why it was important,

00:27:56.884 --> 00:27:57.865
and he had bought into it.

00:27:58.464 --> 00:27:59.646
He was transformed.

00:28:01.839 --> 00:28:01.960
Now,

00:28:01.980 --> 00:28:05.060
this realization is underscored by the

00:28:05.101 --> 00:28:07.162
fact that Yahowah's participation was

00:28:07.241 --> 00:28:09.722
engendered by his son's dyn,

00:28:09.762 --> 00:28:11.804
ability to make informed and rational

00:28:11.824 --> 00:28:14.144
decisions when confronted with the

00:28:14.184 --> 00:28:14.605
evidence.

00:28:14.684 --> 00:28:15.785
And boy, was he ever.

00:28:16.286 --> 00:28:19.207
I can't wait to share my most recent

00:28:19.247 --> 00:28:21.468
translation of the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr

00:28:21.508 --> 00:28:21.928
with you,

